{
  "stem": "16106.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was very-- I thought that was kind of a good warning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you brush your teeth?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finger.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POINTING] With salt, whatever I got.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Brush your teeth, and then with the ice, or with the ice, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always, I always combed my hair, and you know, I learned that looks were quite important.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whatever says is superficial and people-- Americans are obsessed with good looks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Looks were important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you looked neat and you looked somehow presentable, it was easier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't help it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was somewhat easier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you were clean, you felt better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if I had, in the morning, got up and it was-- that cold ice woke me up, my-- it was a better situation, all right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then what we-- as I was saying, we got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was along the harbor and there were ships.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the sailors had their tins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They threw the garbage out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the tins on the bottom were little [? liverwurst ?], the little this and that which we grabbed out and-- so we, we managed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But one day, that thing was over, too, and we're handed, we were handed a, a a bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one interesting thing happened there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, the young [GERMAN] said to me, I have a wonderful surprise for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going on an outing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're coming with me to the city of Danzig.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're going to do as if you carry something for me, which I can't do, but I want you to have an outing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Danzig, the two of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went on a strassenbahn, on a trolley, and the-- I was not meant to be because everybody, with my uniform, I had to stand there in the back with her things.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
